      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 36,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Arataki Itto_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "荒瀧一斗",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "荒瀧一斗因為擁有防轉攻的機制，所以攻擊力需求並不算太高；一斗的重擊傷害佔比非常高，而此武器可以直接提高重擊傷害，因此可以在沒有其餘合適的四五星武器情況下使用此武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "辛焱",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "辛焱在六命後也會擁有防轉攻的機制，且非常依賴重擊，所以也可以在沒有其餘合適的四五星武器情況下讓她使用此武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
